less."],[2506,2566,"And you want to tell me"],[2566,2687,"you care for her now?"],[2706,2766,"Ugh!"],[2766,2926,"How dare you!"],[3020,3236,"If you insult Iris again,"],[3236,3410,"then I will fucking kill you!"],[3410,3582,"Ben, we are best friends!"],[3582,3750,"And you're gonna choose her over me?"],[3750,3830,"Oh!"],[3832,4070,"You are nothing compared to her."],[4092,4312,"She is my everything!"],[4312,4346,"Okay?"],[4366,4458,"Don't go around here"],[4458,4583,"barking like a big dog."],[4600,4670,"Nothing but a little pup"],[4670,4822,"can't keep his pants up."],[4842,4990,"You lost your wife."],[5026,5210,"Now you're gonna take it out on me."],[5242,5390,"What did you just fucking say?"],[5472,5546,"I'm not the one that"],[5566,5645,"stripped down Penny naked"],[5645,5772,"and threw her in your bed."],[5782,5821,"What?"],[5821,6062,"You can't resist some little slut seduction,"],[6090,6181,"and now you're gonna tell me"],[6181,6346,"that you love your wife!"],[6346,6446,"Come on! Bro!"],[6446,6612,"You're fucking pathetic!"],[6752,6820,"Oh!"],[6860,7010,"Shut your fucking mouth!"],[7280,7392,"Fucking do it!"],[7440,7560,"You can't do shit."],[7792,7942,"Within 7 days,"],[7962,8186,"I want his family completely destroyed!"],[8262,8490,"No chance of ever coming back."],[8490,8570,"Yes, sir."],[8620,8752,"In 100 million,"],[8752,8906,"start a worldwide search."],[8930,9182,"I need to find every clue I can of Iris."],[9220,9300,"Yes, sir."],[9420,9500,"Babe,"],[9560,9840,"I won't stop, until I find you."]],"36":[[806,956,"Benjamin has put out a"],[962,1160,"global bounty looking for you."],[1170,1386,"If he's got money to burn in his pocket,"],[1386,1492,"let's help him."],[1532,1700,"Send out some fake leads."],[1742,1952,"I love your bad idea!"],[2872,3026,"Oh, isn't that Benjamin?"],[3100,3212,"The cheating jerk."],[3220,3440,"He's probably to hunt down Iris."],[3526,3794,"Gross! Iris barely escaped that hell,"],[3794,3946,"and he wants to drag her back?"],[3