ing for me,"],[1250,1453,"please tell him I left for the airport"],[1453,1552,"after drinking."],[1620,1700,"Okay."],[2000,2200,"Oh, she just walked here"],[2200,2387,"with some stuff and left."],[2390,2506,"Do you know where she went?"],[2506,2746,"She told me that she just got divorced"],[2746,2926,"and travelling all over the world."],[2926,3011,"So,"],[3011,3096,"I think she told me"],[3096,3306,"that the next step would be Greece."],[3366,3536,"And actually I ordered to her"],[3536,3682,"some custume for gift."],[3682,3860,"So I have her cell phone."],[4206,4520,"No, she won't pick up if she sees it's me."],[4566,4740,"I need a different phone."],[4950,5126,"Can I buy your phone? Take it!"],[5182,5322,"If this isn't enough..."],[5322,5426,"Whatever you want!"],[5426,5506,"Please!"],[5586,5801,"Well, you look so desperate."],[5820,5896,"Fine."]],"40":[[60,192,"Buy me a ticket to Greece."],[192,372,"The earliest you can, now."],[986,1098,"Hello, police."],[1109,1215,"I would like to"],[1215,1391,"report a stolen phone."],[1922,2152,"I told him exactly what you asked."],[2152,2452,"And he's going to the airport now."],[2480,2622,"Okay, thank you."],[3140,3220,"Boss."],[3222,3376,"It turns out that greedy woman"],[3376,3533,"wanted to rip you off,"],[3542,3646,"and framed you for it."],[3676,3702,"No."],[3766,3952,"This is Iris's idea."],[3952,4072,"I know she's here."],[4072,4292,"I know it, I have to find her."],[4452,4592,"Your father ordered me"],[4592,4742,"to bring you home right now."],[4822,5002,"Get out of my way."],[5306,5380,"Benjamin!"]],"41":[[86,166,"Iris."],[250,333,"Iris."],[626,706,"Grandma!"],[910,972,"What are you doing"],[972,1112,"in Paris?"],[1142,1393,"I told you Iris is a good girl,"],[1393,1520,"and you messed up."],[1522,1658,"You should've cherish her."],[1712,1800,"Shame on you!"],[1986,2066,"I..."],[2152,2270,"I know, grandma."],[2370,2500,"It's all my fault."],[2572,2706,"But I can't lose her."],[2800,2880,"Please..."],[2990,3070,"Plea