I'm never giving up on you."],[3690,3740,"You!"],[3748,3830,"Benjamin!"],[3948,4048,"Do you have a bad memory?"],[4190,4304,"Everyone knows you and Iris"],[4304,4460,"aren't split up over just a"],[4460,4566,"misunderstanding."],[4580,4660,"Hmm."]],"50":[[20,100,"Austin!"],[220,386,"Like I told you before,"],[426,720,"this is none of your business, outsider."],[846,940,"Wow!"],[1032,1442,"New flame and old love? Both so impressive!"],[1442,1712,"Iris is really living the good life."],[1792,1860,"The ex looks"],[1860,2026,"passionate and generous."],[2026,2180,"Why Iris divorced him?"],[2212,2282,"Yeah."],[2332,2492,"Shut up!"],[2786,2863,"Let's not fight."],[2863,3000,"We're here to have fun."],[3072,3194,"Mr. Bennett, we appreciate"],[3200,3322,"you being here."],[3342,3472,"Now, if you don't mind-"],[3472,3710,"I thought this was a celebration."],[3766,3882,"How could I just leave?"],[3906,4110,"And weren't we playing a game?"],[4160,4260,"What game were we playing?"],[4470,4641,"Yeah, uh, we're playing"],[4641,4806,"like truth or dare."],[4810,5050,"Whoever the bottle is pointing to"],[5072,5200,"should answer a question."],[5232,5466,"The last spin landed on you!"],[5730,5810,"Fine!"],[5906,5986,"Ask!"],[6066,6226,"I'll ask the question."],[6386,6600,"Why you"],[6702,6950,"and Iris get divorced?"]],"51":[[350,566,"Hmm, good question."],[722,846,"Come on, if you"],[890,1026,"don't want to answer,"],[1126,1206,"just drink."],[1412,1602,"Benjamin, do you even"],[1602,1817,"dare say out loud all the shameful things"],[1817,1897,"you've done?"],[1972,2070,"Because..."],[2160,2256,"Because..."],[2360,2582,"Because I made an unforgivable mistake."],[2860,3080,"I betrayed Iris's trust."],[3172,3382,"Broke the vows I promised her."],[3422,3502,"And..."],[3566,3700,"I killed our baby."],[4020,4122,"I deserved to die."],[4170,4250,"And now..."],[4330,4526,"Now I am doing everything"],[4570,4686,"to win her back,"],[4750,4890,"to have her forgive me,"],[4896,5026,"to give me one more chance."],[5106,5252,"Looks so heartfelt."],[5310,5412,"But it's fake."],[5600,5870,"Cheaters are trash. Unforgivable!"],[6230,6310,"Fine!"],[6386,6480,"My turn."],[6970,7060,"Oh!"],[7142,7222,"What do you know?"],[7234,7330,"Austin!"],[7400,7492,"It landed on you!"],[7570,7730,"You being around Iris"],[7736,7890,"is an coincidence, huh?"],[8100,8312,"You planned all this, didn't you?"],[8326,8432,"So what if I did?"],[8520,8600,"Iris!"],[8650,8726,"Oh!"],[8726,8810,"So you admitted it!"],[8810,8946,"Iris, did you hear that?"],[9020,9246,"He's been lying to you this entire time!"],[9482,9635,"I kept my feelings hidden for her"],[9635,9772,"because she chose you!"],[9822,9897,"What?"],[9897,10005,"And you betrayed her,"],[10046,10162,"destroyed her,"],[10210,10332,"and tore her apart!"],[10486,10557,"Now I have the chance"],[10557,10710,"to show my love for her."],[11146,11312,"Don't be awful, Iris."],[11504,11692,"I said, I'd do anything for you."],[11960,12236,"But I don't want my love become a burden to you."],[12486,12662,"Stop lying to her, scumbag."],[12662,12786,"You're the real hypocrite!"],[12946,13060,"Stop!"],[13186,13390,"Just leave me alone!"]],"52":[[786,866,"Iris!"],[866,1040,"What are you doing here again?"],[1052,1120,"I was worried you weren't"],[1142,1226,"like the food in Paris."],[1226,1306,"So,"],[1342,1470,"I made you your favorite bread!"],[1650,1770,"What happened to your hand?"],[1870,1950,"Oh..."],[2002,2166,"Don't worry about it. It's not a big deal."],[2170,2340,"It doesn't even hurt."],[2372,2526,"Just try the bread, okay?"],[2546,2626,"It's pretty good!"],[2900,3102,"Iris, my love,"],[3102,3252,"no matter what I do,"],[3270,3532,"I still cannot replace him in your heart,"],[3572,3652,"right?"],[3840,4086,"Stop doing things like this."],[4086,4167,"It's useless."],[4167,4282,"I've already told you."],[4294,4440,"There is no us anymore."],[4470,4562,"Are you deaf?"],[4570,4802,"Iris, I am doing everything I can"],[4802,4922,"to make things right."],[4982,5220,"Please, just give me another chance."],[5302,5406,"One more chance?"],[5406,5622,"I have given you so many chances,"],[5622,5830,"and you never valued a single one of them."],[5902,6102,"Where were you when I was sick?"],[6102,6269,"Where were you when I nearly die,"],[6269,6440,"losing our child?"],[6462,6562,"You lied to me"],[6566,6684,"over and over again,"],[6690,6852,"sneaking around with Penny."],[6940,7072,"How dare you stand here"],[7078,7212,"and ask for forgiveness?"],[7342,7446,"Our love?"],[7492,7660,"...is like this glass."],[7810,7946,"Once it breaks,"],[7986,8192,"we are never getting back together."],[8386,8480,"Iris!"],[9082,9252,"It's too late, Benjamin."],[9330,9594,"When you forgot your vows and chased off"],[9594,9760,"to the thrill of cheating,"],[9760,9940,"our marriage was already over."]],"53":[[526,700,"Y, I, uh..."],[762,912,"I'm feeling too hurt."],[930,1012,"I don't think I'll be able to"],[1012,1156,"make it to the office today."],[1186,1286,"You okay?"],[1292,1512,"Need me to come with you to the hospital?"],[1512,1659,"No, no, it's okay."],[1659,1882,"I probably just caught a cold."],[1900,2190,"Then get some rest and take pills, okay?"],[2246,2326,"Okay."],[2992,3228,"So this is what living alone feels like."],[4760,4900,"Wow, smells good!"],[4900,5112,"I must be starving if I'm seeing things."],[5622,5777,"Yeah, definitely a dream."],[6050,6226,"You hungry? I make some pasta."],[6440,6486,"Benjamin!"],[6486,6642,"What are you doing here?"],[6642,6704,"Yvette told me"],[6704,6830,"you weren't feeling well, so..."],[6866,6952,"I got worried."],[6952,7070,"I told you I never"],[7070,7200,"want to see you again!"],[7200,7310,"But you're sick."],[7310,7432,"Go away."],[7440,7570,"Okay, fine!"],[7866,8022,"With your pasta!"],[8052,8140,"Okay!"],[8706,8816,"Take care, Iris."],[8816,8920,"Go!"],[9226,9390,"Benjamin, why don't you get it?"],[9420,9560,"No matter what you do,"],[9566,9706,"I'll never forgive you!"],[9752,9960,"Not now, not ever!"]],"54":[[506,600,"Yvette?"],[900,1130,"Yvette, where are you?"],[1230,1651,"Tried so hard, it got so far."],[1740,2070,"In the end, it doesn't matter."],[2100,2274,"I've had too far"],[2334,2494,"to lose it all."],[2574,2880,"In the end, it doesn't matter."],[2890,2960,"Will you marry me?"],[3120,3200,"Yes!"],[5306,5446,"It doesn't matter."],[6742,6822,"Iris!"],[7652,7804,"I know I don't deserve"],[7810,7922,"your forgiveness."],[7960,8090,"But I promise,"],[8110,8246,"I will spend the rest of my life"],[8246,8366,"making it up to you."],[8412,8510,"Please!"],[8650,8820,"Please come back to me!"],[9072,9152,"I..."],[9366,9602,"Finally found you both!"],[9680,9900,"Penny, what the hell happened to you?"],[9940,10192,"This is all your fault! Iris."],[10210,10337,"People are cursing me in the street"],[10337,10440,"because of you!"],[10466,10495,"No!"],[10552,10718,"I'm gonna make you pay for you've done!"],[10718,10819,"You bitch!"]],"55":[[10,92,"Ah!"],[280,360,"Ben?"],[380,452,"Ben!"],[452,546,"Why?"],[671,846,"I promise"],[846,1050,"I'll never let you get hurt."],[1300,1402,"Benjamin."],[1402,1622,"You mess with my feelings!"],[1622,1722,"You bastard!"],[1728,1906,"I'm gonna fucking kill you!"],[2290,2400,"I'm gonna kill you!"],[2553,2652,"Ben! Ben!"],[2652,2762,"Please, Ben!"],[3802,3947,"Son of a bitch!"],[4130,4210,"Ben?"],[4212,4320,"Iris, are you okay?"],[4352,4632,"It's not me, it's Ben! Save him."],[4632,4730,"He's bleeding out!"],[4730,4765,"Don't worry!"],[4765,4872,"An ambulance is on the way!"],[5072,5186,"Iris!"],[5258,5324,"Please..."],[5372,5640,"Don't leave me."],[5846,6010,"Ben! Ben, please!"],[6022,6186,"Please, the ambulance is on its way."],[6186,6442,"Ben! Please don't leave me!"],[7566,7711,"Benjamin lost so much blood."],[7711,7826,"What if he dies?"],[7826,7942,"Listen, Iris!"],[7982,8100,"He'll be all right."],[8512,8600,"Have you, uh..."],[8770,8906,"Have you decided to go back to him?"],[9540,9620,"Uh..."],[9666,9764,"I don't know."],[10262,10460,"It's okay."]],"56":[[640,730,"How is he, doctor?"],[786,1026,"Luckily, no vital organs were hit."],[1040,1186,"The wounds aren't deep."],[1276,1460,"He just lost a lot of blood."],[1460,1700,"He will recover with proper rest."],[1710,1832,"Thank you, doctor."],[2770,2850,"Are you okay?"],[3972,4172,"Iris, if I could..."],[4240,4540,"I would freeze this moment, forever."],[5372,5482,"Get some rest."],[5510,5622,"Hmm, okay."],[6622,6778,"If we hadn't lost this baby,"],[6784,6930,"would we be this happy now?"],[7010,7090,"But..."],[7140,7370,"There is no if in life."],[8400,8570,"We should go back to the room now."]],"57":[[222,446,"Iris, I knew you still cared for me."],[462,610,"Thanks to your devotion,"],[616,720,"I fully recovered."],[770,870,"And today,"],[876,1212,"I'm proposing to you all over again."],[1252,1466,"Let's rewrite our story!"],[1890,2036,"Has your doctor cleared you"],[2036,2162,"for discharge?"],[2280,2426,"Well, you know, I've fully recovered."],[2512,2632,"Thank you for taking care of me!"],[2742,2952,"Don't misunderstand."],[3006,3126,"You got hurt because of me."],[3126,3397,"I'm just trying to"],[3397,3506,"make sure you're okay."],[3506,3606,"Now that you're fine,"],[3606,3692,"I should go."],[3692,3950,"No, no, no! Come with me."],[3980,4040,"What?"],[4092,4172,"You'll see."],[4340,4384,"Ben!"],[5462,5580,"What's this?"],[5686,5830,"I bought this racetrack."],[5940,6063,"I had it remodeled"],[6063,6226,"just like Quantum Raceway."],[6372,6552,"I even had the car shipped in from home."],[6662,6742,"Iris,"],[6830,6940,"I did all for you."],[7070,7150,"Why?"],[7210,7512,"Because, Iris, I can't live without you."],[7546,7678,"Let's forget about the past"],[7684,7806,"and start over right here,"],[7832,7922,"right now."],[8112,8214,"Iris Kensington."],[9172,9306,"Will you marry me"],[9338,9400,"again?"]],"58":[[332,426,"Iris!"],[426,509,"A ringing bell can"],[509,666,"never keep people unknown."],[722,886,"I will never marry you again."],[892,972,"But..."],[1010,1146,"But you stayed with me at the hospital"],[1146,1244,"the entire time."],[1300,1400,"I thought..."],[1406,1560,"I thought that meant you forgave me."],[1586,1850,"I stayed because you saved my life."],[1930,2186,"It changes nothing between us."],[2266,2352,"But Iris,"],[2446,2666,"I really love you."],[2740,2902,"You are like my oxygen."],[2982,3140,"I can't breathe without you."],[3300,3442,"Why can't you just let this go?"],[3442,3629,"Because I can't let it go!"],[3760,3926,"Benjamin, when we got married,"],[3942,4156,"I buried a letter under the tree"],[4156,4246,"in our yard,"],[4246,4429,"I planned for us to dig it up"],[4429,4600,"on our fiftieth anniversary."],[4670,4832,"That day will never come."],[4863,4997,"I'll go get it right now."],[4997,5118,"I'll have it flown here."],[5118,5186,"I'll call the jet-"],[5186,5291,"What's the point?"],[5410,5570,"Even if the letter is still there,"],[5570,5704,"our marriage is broken."],[5809,5874,"Fine."],[6134,6231,"Iris,"],[6334,6503,"I know I messed up."],[6585,6825,"I know I broke our vows."],[7070,7187,"Losing you..."],[7342,7520,"is the punishment I deserve."],[8265,8495,"To repay you for donating your kidney."],[8695,9001,"I know money means nothing to you, but..."],[9051,9259,"I need a clean break."]],"59":[[46,174,"Ben, thank you"],[174,330,"for once loving me."],[468,642,"But I'll walk alone."],[792,922,"Just..."],[922,1082,"Hold me one more time!"],[3366,3446,"Goodbye!"],[3560,3742,"My first love."],[5780,5890,"Is that a snowflake?"],[5942,6060,"From the South Pole."],[6120,6232,"You serious?"],[6232,6302,"Mm-hmm."],[6350,6504,"I preserved it in a 1% of"],[6504,6672,"Polyvinyl Acetal Resin."],[6682,6822,"It'll last forever."],[7022,7102,"Iris."],[7422,7502,"Come with me."],[10406,10504,"I hope Benjamin and I"],[10504,10640,"will grow old together."]],"60":[[32,132,"Penny was right."],[212,356,"The second I betrayed Iris"],[356,472,"with another woman,"],[630,886,"I forfeited any right to her mercy."],[1560,1646,"Iris..."],[1800,1946,"It's been 10 years."],[1960,2070,"Are you doing well?"],[2070,2206,"Mommy, come on."],[2452,2602,"Hi, baby!"],[2710,2822,"-Yes. -Yeah?"],[3332,3412,"Hmm..."],[3486,3612,"Baby, you like puppies, right?"],[3612,3670,"Yes!"],[3738,3910,"What if daddy barked like a dog?"],[3910,3990,"Yes."],[4680,4766,"Why are you laughing?"],[4832,4946,"Maybe because you're cute."],[6086,6302,"Karma's wheel has turned."],[6402,6532,"Justice served!"],[6660,6942,"Being alone is the fate I deserve."],[7052,7132,"Babe..."],[7186,7342,"I wish you happiness."],[7506,7612,"From now on,"],[7680,7760,"I..."],[7820,7960,"won't bother you anymore."]]}